               <p>I am wife of 
               <persName id="t17850914-99-person1080">
                  James
                   Campbell
               <interp inst="t17850914-99-person1080" type="surname" value="Campbell"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850914-99-person1080" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850914-99-person1080" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , on Monday the 18th of July last, about half past nine in the morning I was sitting at breakfast in the five parlour, the prisoner was at the door of the side parlour, I saw him put the box under his arm, and I ran and caught hold of his coat with one arm, and with the other caught hold of the box; I am sure the man that was brought back was the same man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17850914-99-person1081">
                  JAMES
                   CAMPBELL
               <interp inst="t17850914-99-person1081" type="surname" value="CAMPBELL"></interp>
